  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-04 synthetic)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. Model Risk Level 3. Thirteen credibility factors are evaluated; twelve are assessed with full data. One factor — Equivalency of input parameters — carries factorStatus 'not-assessed' on the basis that the assessment team judged it inapplicable to a computational-only study with no physical test article, but encoded the status as 'not-assessed' rather than 'not-applicable', leaving a material epistemic gap at MRL 3.",
