    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors were assessed; the majority meet or approach required levels at MRL 3. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification on model inputs was completed. The team accepted the package on the basis that the unassessed Equivalency of input parameters factor was judged inapplicable to a computational-only study, though this judgment was not formally encoded as 'not-applicable'. The remaining assessed factor gaps are documented and accepted under Low assurance level with compensating mitigations noted in the validation report.",
